  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流系统的核心流转图，从追踪号开始，经过库存、仓库，再到车队管理，最后闭环回来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是追踪号。那追踪号之后直接连到库存节点吗？还是中间有其他环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，追踪号之后就是库存水位，这是查询库存的第一步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把追踪号节点和库存节点连上了。接下来库存应该指向仓库对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，库存确认后就要确定是哪个仓库出货。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接。我注意到这里有两个仓库节点，是同一个仓库的不同状态，还是不同的仓库？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是两个不同的仓库，第一个是指定出货仓，第二个是实际调度的仓库，有时候会有跨仓调拨。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我把两个仓库节点串起来了。第二个仓库之后应该连到车队管理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，仓库确定后就要分配车队进行配送。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "车队管理节点已加上。这里后面又出现一个仓库节点，是返程还是什么意思？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这是中转仓的概念，车队可能需要把货先送到中转仓库，再二次分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，中转仓加上了。后面又连回车队管理，是二次派车的意思？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，中转仓之后要重新分配最后一公里配送的车队。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "二次车队管理节点已连接。接下来是追踪号节点，这里是要更新追踪状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，配送启动后要生成新的追踪状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我看到后面还有两个追踪号节点，是状态递进的关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，一个是配送中状态，一个是已签收状态，最后签收状态要闭环回到最初的追踪号，表示整个生命周期完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，三个追踪状态节点串联完成，最后闭环连回起点。整个流程看起来是一个完整的物流追踪闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这就是我们要的：从下单查库存，到仓库调度、车队配送、中转、最后一公里，最后签收闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程图已完成，一共9个节点，从追踪号出发经过库存、两个仓库、两次车队管理，最终通过三个追踪状态节点闭环。需要调整什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
